# MediSafe QA Audit Checklist

- [/] Open `http://localhost:3000` and assess the landing page (Note: App started directly on dashboard, skipping landing page. Investigating reset.)
- [ ] Complete Onboarding Wizard:
    - [ ] Click 'Get Started'
    - [ ] Enter Name
    - [ ] Select 'Someone else'
    - [ ] Add 'Aspirin' 500mg daily at 08:00
- [ ] Dashboard Check:
    - [ ] Medication displayed correctly
    - [ ] Adherence ring check
    - [ ] Interaction alert check
- [ ] Add Medication from Dashboard:
    - [ ] Add 'Warfarin' 5mg daily
- [ ] Safety Section:
    - [ ] Verify interaction detection (Aspirin + Warfarin)
- [ ] AI Chat:
    - [ ] Ask "Can I take Aspirin and Warfarin together?"
    - [ ] Verify response
- [ ] Settings:
    - [ ] Toggle notification preference
- [ ] UI/UX Audit & Bug Hunting:
    - [x] Bug: Dashboard shows "No meds added yet" but also says "3 of 4 doses taken today" and shows 75% adherence.
    - [ ] Check for glitches, broken links, non-functional buttons
    - [ ] Evaluate spacing, contrast, and layout
